<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 1in;
        }
        
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
            font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #059669;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .document-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #047857;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #047857;
            margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-left: 4px solid #059669;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }
        
        .subsection-header {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
            margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .content-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        .bullet-point {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .bullet-point::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: -15px;
            color: #059669;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .vision-box {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-left: 4px solid #059669;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .vision-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #047857;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .company-logo {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #047857;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="document-title">{{title}}</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Strategic Vision for AI-Powered Document Generation</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section-header">Mission Statement</div>
    <div class="content-text">To democratize professional document creation by providing businesses of all sizes with AI-powered tools that generate high-quality, branded documents in minutes, not hours.</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Product Philosophy</div>
    <div class="content-text">MM Docs transforms the traditional document creation process from a time-consuming, manual task into an intelligent, automated experience. We believe every business deserves access to professional-grade documentation that reflects their brand identity and communicates their message effectively.</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Core Value Propositions</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Speed & Efficiency:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Generate professional documents in under 2 minutes</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Eliminate repetitive formatting and content creation tasks</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Reduce document creation time by 90% compared to manual methods</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Quality & Professionalism:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">AI-powered content generation ensures consistent, professional language</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Comprehensive template library covers all business document needs</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Automatic brand integration maintains visual consistency</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Accessibility & Ease of Use:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Intuitive interface requires no design or technical expertise</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Category-based navigation simplifies document selection</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Detailed form inputs guide users through the creation process</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Product Capabilities</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Document Categories:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">HR & Employment: Offer letters, contracts, policies, certificates</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Legal & Compliance: NDAs, agreements, terms of service, privacy policies</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Sales & Marketing: Proposals, quotations, company profiles, pitch decks</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Finance & Accounting: Invoices, receipts, purchase orders, financial reports</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Operations & Admin: Policies, procedures, audit reports, compliance documents</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>AI-Powered Features:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Intelligent content generation based on user inputs</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Context-aware language adaptation for different document types</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Automatic formatting and structure optimization</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Brand-consistent styling and visual elements</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Technical Architecture</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>AI Integration:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">OpenRouter API for advanced language model access</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Custom prompt engineering for document-specific content</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Intelligent template matching and content adaptation</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Brand Management:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Comprehensive brand kit system for logos, colors, fonts</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Automatic brand application across all document types</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Consistent visual identity maintenance</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Target Users</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Primary Users:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Small business owners creating professional documentation</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Freelancers and consultants requiring branded materials</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">HR professionals managing employee documentation</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Sales teams generating client-facing documents</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Use Cases:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Startup founder creating investor pitch decks and legal documents</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">HR manager generating offer letters and employment contracts</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Sales representative creating customized proposals and quotations</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Consultant developing professional service agreements</div>
    
    <div class="vision-box">
        <div class="vision-title">Success Vision</div>
        <div class="content-text">By 2025, MM Docs will be recognized as the leading AI-powered document generation platform, trusted by over 100,000 businesses worldwide to create professional, branded documents that drive business success and enhance professional communication.</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="company-logo">MM Docs</div>
        <div>Professional Document Generation Platform</div>
        <div>AI-Powered Business Solutions</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>